title: Create test project
message:
Create test project

Created a fresh project using the "Android Test Project"
wizard in Eclipse.  Used all defaults except as follows:
- Project Name: WebShortcutAppTest
- Verify Test Target is WebShortcutApp

title: Initial Commit
message:
Initial Commit

Created a fresh project using the "New Android Application"
wizard in Eclipse.  Used all defaults except as follows:
- Application Name: Web Shortcut
- Project Name:     WebShortcutApp
- Package Name:     com.abcodeworks.webshortcutapp
- Theme: Holo Light
- Uncheck "Create Activity" on "Configure Project" screen.
